ISLAMABAD, Jan 14 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif on Tuesday expressed grief over the death of Zafarullah Mengal, the son of late Sardar Attaullah Mengal and brother of Sardar Akhtar Mengal.
The prime minister, in a statement, prayed to Allah Almighty for peace for the departed soul and strength for the bereaved family to bear the loss.
